quran[29]{c,v,t}:
  16,1,"Onyankopͻn ahyεdeε no aba, enti εmma mo mmpere ho. Kronkron Hene ne no; Ɔkorͻn kyεn deε wͻ’de bata Neho no"
  16,2,"Ɔnam N’ahyԑdeԑ so ma Soro abͻfoͻ no de Honhom (Adiyisεm) no siane ba Nenkoa no mu nea Ɔpε so sε: “Momͻ (adasamma) kͻkͻ sε: “Awurade foforͻ biara nni hͻ ka Me ho, enti monsuro Me”"
  16,3,"Ɔde nokorε no na abͻ soro ne asaase, Ɔyε Okokuroko korͻn paa kyεn deε wͻ’de bata Neho no"
  16,4,"Ɔbͻͻ nipa firi ahobaeε mu, na hwε sε ͻno ne otiafoɔ pefee"
  16,5,"Ɛna W’abͻ nyεmmoa nso ama mo; wͻn ho no monya (ntaadeε a) εma mo ͻhyew, san (nya) mfasoͻ pii fri wͻn ho; na wͻn mu bi nso mowe (wͻn nnam)"
  16,6,Monya wͻn ho anigyeε nso wͻ berε a mode wͻn reba fie anyumerε ne εberε a mode wͻn rekͻ adidi anͻpa
  16,7,"Wͻ’soa moadesoa nso dekͻ nkuro so a, anka mobεbrε moho paa ansa na moaduru hͻ. Nokorε sε mo Wura Nyankopͻn yε Ayεmyε Hene, Ɔne Mmͻborͻhunufoͻ Hene"
  16,8,"(W’abͻ) apͻnkͻ ne mfunumu-pͻnkͻ ne mfunumu, sεdeε mobεtena wͻn so, na asan ayε afεfεdeε (ama mo); na Ɔbͻ adeε nso a monnnim"
  16,9,"Onyankopͻn na εyε N’asεdeε sε Ɔkyerε kwan tenee no; na akwan no bi nso wͻ hͻ a amane. Sε εyε Nepε a, anka Ɔbεkyerε mo nyinaa kwan (tenenee no)"
  16,10,"Ɔno na Osiane nsuo fri soro a emu bi na monom, εna ebi nso na yεdema nnua a mo nyεmmoa die no nso (nyini)"
  16,11,"(Ɔsan nso) de ma mfudeε ne ngo nnua ne akyiresua nnua, ne bobe ne nnuaba ahodoͻ nyini ma mo. Nokorε sε, nsεnkyerεnee wͻ woi nom mu dema nnipa a wͻ’dwen"
  16,12,"Ɛna W’abrε anadwo ne adekyeε ase ama mo, εna awia ne bosome ne nsonomma nso brε wͻn ho ase wͻ N’ahyεdeε mu. Nokorε sε nsεnkyerεnee wͻ woi mu dema wͻn a wͻ’dwen"
  16,13,"Deε W’adua ama mo wͻ asaase soͻ no nso gu ahodoͻ sononko-sononko. Nokorε sε, nsεnkyerεnee wͻ woi mu dema wͻn a wͻ’kaekaeε"
  16,14,"Ɔno na W’abrε ͻpo ase sεdeε mobedi emu nam mono, na moayi emu agudeε a mode hyε. Na wohunu nsuom hyεn sε εnam mu, sεdeε mobεhwehwε N’adom, ne sεdeε mobeyi (Onyankopͻn) ayε"
  16,15,"Ɛna Ɔde mmepͻ asisi asaase no so pintinn sεdeε εmma no nnwoso mo, εna (W’ayε) nsubͻnten ne akwan sεdeε mobenya kwan kyerε"
  16,16,"Ɛna (W’ayε) nsohyεdeε, (wͻ asaase so), εna (W’ayε) nsoromma a wͻ’de hunu kwan"
  16,17,"Enti Nea Ɔbͻͻ adeε no, obia ͻmmͻͻ (hwee) ne no na εsε? Adεn monkaekae"
  16,18,"Sε mokan Nyankopͻn adom a monnhunu ano. Nokorε sε, Onyankopͻn ne Bͻnefakyε Hene, Ɔne Mmͻborͻhunufoͻ Hene"
  16,19,Onyankopͻn Nim deε mode suma ne deε moda no adie (nyinaa)
  16,20,"Wͻn a wͻ’fri Nyankopͻn akyi sufrε wͻn no ntumi mmͻ hwee, na wͻn ara nso yεbͻͻ wͻn"
  16,21,"(Wͻ’yε) awufoͻ, wͻ’nnte ase, na wͻ’nnim εberε korͻ a yebenyane wͻn (afri awufuͻ mu)"
  16,22,"Mo Nyankopͻn no yε Awurade baako. Wͻn a wͻ’nnye Daakye no nnie no, wͻn akoma kyiri (sε wͻ’bεte sε Nyankopͻn yε baako), na wͻ’yε ahomasoͻ"
  16,23,"Akyinnyeε biara nni ho sε Onyankopͻn Nim deε wͻ’de suma ne deε wͻ’da no adie (nyinaa). Nokorε sε, Ɔmpε wͻn a wͻ’yε ahomasoͻ no asεm"
  16,24,"Sε yεka kyerε wͻn sε: ”Ɛdeεn na mo Wura Nyankopͻn asiane (ama Nkͻmhyεni) a?” Deε wͻ’ka nesε: “Tetefoͻ no anansesεm “"
  16,25,"Wͻ’bεsoa wͻn adesoa no pεpεεpε wͻ Wusͻreε Da no, na εno akyiri no wͻn asan asoa wͻn a wͻ’yeraa wͻn no a nimdeε biara nni mu no nso adesoa. Nokorε sε, adesoa bͻne paa na wͻ’bεsoa no"
  16,26,"Ampa sε, wͻn a wͻ’dii wͻn anim kan no pam (apam bͻne tiaa wͻn asomafoͻ no), nanso Onyankopͻn fri wͻn dan no fapem no ase dwiri gui maa εdan no mmͻsoͻ no fri soro beguu wͻn so; asotwee no fri faako a wͻ’nnim baa wͻn so"
  16,27,"Afei Wusͻreε da no, Obegu wͻn anim ase na W’aka akyerε wͻn sε: ”M’ahokafoͻ no a wͻn ho nti motan (nkͻmhyεfoͻ no ne agyidiefoͻ no, san) ko tiaa wͻn no wͻ hen? “Wͻn a yama wͻn nimdeε no bεka sε: ”Nokorε, animguaseε ne ͻhaw bͻne bεka boniayεfoͻ no nnε da yi"
  16,28,"“Wͻn a Soro abͻfoͻ yi wͻn nkwa aberε a wͻ’ayε bͻne atia wͻn kraa no, (wͻ’bԑpatu) abrԑ wͻn ho ase (aka sε): “Na yenni dwuma bͻne biara“. (Soro abͻfoͻ no beyi wͻn ano sε): “Daabi, nokorε sε, Onyankopͻn Nim dwuma a modiiε nyinaa.“"
  16,29,Enti monwura Amanehunu gya no pono no mu nkͻtena hͻ. Ԑhͻ yε asetena bͻne paa dema ahomasoͻfoͻ no